As a user
I can signup/login
I can add/view/delete ingredients I have in my pantry
I can view/add/delete recipes
I can see recipes that I can use with the ingredients I currently have in stock
I can review recipes
If I select a recipe, the ingredients necessary for it will be removed from my pantry   
  --> create Meal? -> user_id, recipe_id
  --> 
I can recommend a recipe on the site/fb/tw/email
I can choose what type of cuisine im interested in

